Description: This 2018 Gibson Memphis ES-335 Traditional in Vintage Ebony has around 1 hour play time and is in near mint condition. Nice dark rosewood fingerboard on this one. It includes all case candy, COA and OHSC. Asking $2499 OBO! When it comes to electric guitars, the Gibson ES-335 is easily one of the most legendary designs. Born in the late 1950s, much of the design of the 335 has gone unchanged throughout the decades. This Gibson Memphis ES-335 Traditional is no exception. However, this semi-hollowbody electric guitar does add touches such as titanium saddles, Burstbucker humbucking pickups, and an ABR-1 bridge to bring the instrument into the modern day. Add in the ES-335 Traditional's vintage-correct wiring, and you have a semi-hollowbody electric guitar with the best of yesterday and today. Title: 2018 Gibson Memphis ES-335 Traditional Vintage Ebony
